 immediately and supportive care rendered as necessary.', 'Synergism', 'Caution is advised when opioids are used concomitantly with serotonergic agents such as selective serotonin reuptake inhibitors (SSRIs), serotonin and norepinephrine reuptake inhibitors (SNRIs), monoamine oxidase inhibitors (MAOIs), tricyclic antidepressants (TCAs), other antidepressants/psychotropic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/4834/', '', 'Rimegepant, Eptinezumab, Dihydroergotamine, Ubrogepant, Ergotamine, Galcanezumab, Atogepant, Methysergide, Erenumab, Fremanezumab', 'Naltrexone, Opium, Dextropropoxyphene, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone', 1767369485);
